c4c4aab905","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3450,"content":"我这还进步呢,我10k的薪资拿了6年,今年刚被裁,直接转行,当保安去,不在这行卷了","createdAt":"2024-07-09T09:38:49"},{"id":"01963df1-a917-7232-b3f1-fafae4c8fc3f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":629,"content":"我9.5每月还老家房贷2800，济南房租1000，比你挣得还少，一个月一分存不下，哎","createdAt":"2024-07-09T09:43:04"},{"id":"01963df1-a964-7309-9c93-8a29e482dccd","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7226,"content":"5年 9k 中专","createdAt":"2024-07-12T10:29:12"},{"id":"01963df1-a960-70f9-8aaf-b84ee5669e05","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5462,"content":"兄弟是真的去干保安了？还是开玩笑","createdAt":"2024-07-16T13:52:59"}]